{
 "name": "RPlog_Neutral_Ground",
 "title": "Neutral Ground",
 "summary": "In Lynae Cassius's small cabin on Caspar, the doctor convenes a fraught tea-table summit she has been holding piecemeal: the Jedi ambassador Enb'Zik on one side, and the Sith Lord Malign, going by Tyler, with his evasive maroon-cloaked agent Malif, captain of the Maven, on the other. Over endless cups of tea and clouds of cigarette smoke, the group circles the fate of Dac and its shipyards, the failures of both the Republic and the Empire, and the shadowy outside influence that may be steering the galaxy toward ruin. Enb'Zik refuses to trust the Sith even as he concedes the logic of cooperating, the interim Presav Mahon looking on. The debate spirals without resolution until Enb'Zik agrees to travel with them to Aquarius, tabling the deeper disagreements for the urgent crisis at hand.",
